            <bug_when>2009-03-04 20:53:02 +0100</bug_when>
            <thetext>When trying to build a native application or native demo in the demobrowser the build contains a lot of stuff only needed for GUI application. This is the result of a forced inclusion of the base.json or the json generated by &quot;genjson.py&quot; in the demobrowser. This also means a comparable slow load time of basic low-level demos or application generated by the current build system.</thetext>
          </long_desc>
